simple.name: AWGN Noise Power
simple.description: The power of the AWGN noise

simple.name: Fading type
simple.description: Specifies the fading type. Valid values are "None" and "Ricean"

simple.name: Envelope Fading Only
simple.description: If set to "True" fading doesn't affect the phase of the signal. Valid values "True" and "False"

simple.name: K Fading factor
simple.description: This is the Ricean K fading factor, 0 implies Rayleigh fading

simple.name: Max doppler rate
simple.description: The maximum doppler rate in terms of (divided by) the sample rate.

simplesequence.name: port_list
simplesequence.description: Returns a sequence of strings with the names of the available Provides ports
